\par }{\fs22\expnd0\expndtw-2\cf1\insrsid14311781\charrsid8331440 \endash  Te most \'e9ppen kik\'e9pzel engem kommand\'f3snak?! \endash  h\'f6rd\'fclt Brayden.
\par }{\fs22\cf1\insrsid14311781\charrsid8331440 \endash  Elv\'e9gre f\'e9rfi vagy, nemde?!
